Date: 1999-09-10

Title: Gravitational Stability and Renormalization-Group Flow

Authors: Kostas Skenderis and Paul K. Townsend

Comments: 12p, Latex; v2

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B468 (1999) 46-51

First-order `Bogomol'nyi' equations are found for dilaton domain walls ofD-dimensional gravity with the general dilaton potential admitting a stableanti-de Sitter vacuum. Implications for renormalization group flow in theholographically dual field theory are discussed.